summary: DAY 4 of the Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE! The next 13 episodes that is going to be streamed (from Season 1) will...
body:
DAY 4 of the Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE!

The next 13 episodes that is going to be streamed (from Season 1) will feature the debut of Jigglypuff, James’s arranged marriage, the birth of Togepi, Todd Snap’s introduction, the evolution of Charmander to Charmeleon to Charizard all in this rotation, and much much more!

The episode set will show 4 times just so you won’t miss it depending on your schedule: 10am | 3:58pm | 9:42pm | 3:26am (PDT, UTC−07:00)

Watching with Twitch chat could be the best (or worst) experience you’ll ever have! But if you want a more comfy chat experience, feel free to talk/chat about the marathon in my Pokémon Discord server PokéTōku —> Invite link here :)

blog.name: pokegodsandmissingno
blog.title: P̵o̵K̸é̴G̸o̸D̷s̸ and Frightful Things to Come?
blog.description: There is a growing desire and expectation of humans here on Earth in making full contact with PoKéMoN who are still unknown. Back in 1995, when I saw my first UPM (Unindexed Pocket Monster), I found out very quickly that other people thought you were totally crazy if you said you saw such things. The world has changed quite a bit since then when I was a child. In fact, in late 1997, a poll taken in Kanto shows that for the first time ever, more than fifty percent of residents now believe in PokéGODS's. Since then, there have been polls that put the figure at over eighty percent or more.

caption:
“ On Newmoon Island, Darkrai dreams. ”

Dream Eater is a mature gameverse Pokemon RP with regular events and a heavy basis on themes of nightmares and shared dreaming. Something strange is happening across every Pokemon region, an unexplained phenomenon drawing people across the world into strange nightmares and dreamscapes – with each other. There’s been an effort to make a network of everyone experiencing the phenomenon, but whether any truths will be found is as of yet undetermined.

We are 18+, set on discord, and have modes for both para rp and ic chat. Come check out our pages for more info! 🌠🌙

blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!
